    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. The power is managed by a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. The suspension geometry remains tight, featuring upgraded bushings for improved lateral stability. While the aesthetics reflect its age, the drivetrain and chassis are dialed in for a precise, analog driving experience.",
